Where do you think you are going
following someone else's map?

9
00:00:36,662 --> 00:00:40,458
An insightful crow comes along

10
00:00:40,541 --> 00:00:43,669
to tear up the map

11
00:00:43,753 --> 00:00:47,173
Now open your eyes

12
