16
00:01:05,441 --> 00:01:08,903
Fighting Dreamers follow what they believe

17
00:01:08,986 --> 00:01:12,573
Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way

18
00:01:12,656 --> 00:01:15,701
Right here right now (Bang)
Hit it straight like a line drive!

19
00:01:15,785 --> 00:01:19,747
Right here right now (Burn) We're
gonna do it and do our best!

